    • edu.ncsu.csc.itrust.beans.forms.EditOfficeVisitForm

  • public class EditOfficeVisitForm
extends java.lang.Object
    A form to contain data coming from editing an office visit. A form is a bean, kinda. You could say that it's a ?form? of a bean :) Think of a form as a real-life administrative form that you would fill out to get something done, not necessarily making sense by itself.
